reviewText: Good 3D, but there goes another 45 minutes and $13.00 I'll never get back again! Boring lame plot and very poor script... was this written by a child??  Watching this disc was like viewing someone playing a video game... Minecraft comes to mind?!  So, if sitting back and watching a boring game of a gnome wondering around a castle, going from room to room (like game levels/maps), then this is for YOU???!!!!!
Bought this for a gift and recipient seemed pleased with it; however I have no first - hand knowledge of its content...seller was excellent!
